snippet.title: Amber Heard SAYS NO to DELAY! Wants it NOW! (Johnny Depp, Amber Heard 2021)
snippet.description:
Amber Heard has filed her response papers to say that she does not want the court to delay their January 2021 dates and says Johnny Depp KNEW in advance of his filming dates. 

Heard says NO to DELAY! (Johnny Depp, Amber Heard 2021)

LINK: https://www.fairfaxcounty.gov/circuit/sites/circuit/files/assets/documents/pdf/high-profile/depp%20v%20heard/cl-2019-2911-def-opp-to-plaintiff-mot-for-continuance-9-4-2020.pdf
